{"type": "article", "id": 28624, "title": "这个只有一条柜台的手表店，产品也同样简洁", "description": "从手表设计到店铺都流露出中性的审美。", "date": "2016-06-23T14:43:31Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1130, "name": "手表"}, {"id": 10455, "name": "店铺"}, {"id": 117, "name": "纽约"}, {"id": 29349, "name": "Studio Mills"}, {"id": 29350, "name": "Larsson & Jennings"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 131, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702163059R5Az6guLxyStIXeP.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>当实体店开始发展电商业务时，也有电商发展线下业务，英国手表品牌 <a href=\"http://www.larssonandjennings.com\">Larsson &amp; Jennings</a> 就是这样。品牌成立 4 年后，他们在伦敦和纽约开了 3 家店。</p>\n<p>这与不景气的腕表市场相悖，Larsson &amp; Jennings 目前推出了 3 个系列共 39 款手表，价格主要在 200 到 300 欧元之间，属于中高端市场。细看 Larsson &amp; Jennings 的手表会发现，三个系列对应了圆形或方形的三种表盘，形状复古，只是改变了边框的颜色或材料，结合了传统和时尚简洁的特征。手表统一在瑞士制作，暗示着传统的精良工艺，这也解释了价格较高的原因。特别在于表带是可替换的，Larsson &amp; Jennings 有 15 款不同颜色的皮带去替代原有的金属表链，让这些表显得非常灵活而年轻。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163049LaAtKVZ4CmDOMbwe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8425\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163053rhTjMEKVgJnCdW4t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.51944444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163053gRUWjq8fC0GXmrO5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65648051\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021630547lJemfauXHgsW9F4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.43796296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>Larsson &amp; Jennings 的线下店倒是更能体现简洁的特征。三家店的空间都很小，最新在曼哈顿巴勒克街（Bleecker Street）的这家只有 470 平方英尺（44 平方米），沿着狭长空间放置一个很长的展示台，是盒子一样的形状。所有手表在柜台上呈悬臂式展示，一字排开，非常清晰明了。除了几款昂贵的手表罩上的玻璃罩，其余全部暴露在外，也让人有很强的参与度。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163054pzJXmivg7Qj3uPfB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163055mWAipwuDj6L34lcY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163055zWQ8bKajwpZBdc5m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163056Qvowsmu6akgCNZ2E.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>店内基本保持了黑白分明的两种颜色，只摆放了镜子等简单的家具，甚至没有游客坐下来的地方或彩色的装饰，也使柜台成为最中心的地方。黑色的柜台、黑色线条灯和大片白墙之间形成的简单的几何对比，流露出一种中性的审美。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163056iBrZVnXsU4xgHjNl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163057jN6uB8a9ThEvmCAz.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.40064103\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">有趣的是这家店开在了具有波西米亚时尚风格的巴勒克街（Bleecker Street），这家店的极简风格就成为另一种对照。</p>\n<p class=\"\">同样的极简风格延续在海报和网站设计上。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070216305790B3G1VCca2lTmN5.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163058HQ5GNYALWKeZ7qUm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.43796296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163058uFLyPVNcl2pesHaq.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.43796296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">图片来自 <a href=\"http://www.dezeen.com/2016/06/20/larsson-jennings-minimal-watch-boutique-new-york-west-village-interior-design/\">dezeen</a>、<a href=\"http://www.larssonandjennings.com/\">Larsson &amp; Jennings</a></p>\n\n"}